{t:E-0104 (A) ALL HEAVENS DECLARE}
{st:}
:E-0104

Chord A

All Heaven declares
The glory of the risen Lord,
Who can compare
With the beauty of the Lord.

Forever Thou wilt be
The Lamb upon the throne.
I gladly bow my knee
And worship Thee alone.

I will proclaim
The glory of the risen Lord,
Who once was slain
To reconcile man to God.



{genre:Praise}
